Here is the code for a function `clean_column` that performs all of these tasks:
```julia
function clean_column(col)
    # Convert to lowercase.
    col = lowercase(col);
    # Strip leading and trailing whitespaces.
    col = strip(col);
    # Replace any spaces or hyphens with an underscore.
    col = replace(col, " " => "_");
    col = replace(col, "-" => "_");
    return col;
end
```
Usage: `clean_column("My Column")`
